            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Sabinus bis IIviralis <lb n="2"/>et <expan><abbr>patr</abbr><ex>onus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>H</abbr><ex>adriani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>robetae</ex></expan> ob <expan><abbr>honor</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>flamoni <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> Naesi Sabini <lb n="4"/>nepotis sui cryptam vetus<lb break="no" n="5"/>tate dilapsam pecunia su<lb break="no" n="6"/>a reformavit et exalti<lb break="no" n="7"/>avit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei aneinander passende Fragmente erhalten. Drobeta ab 123/124 municipium, ab 191/211 colonia.</p>
            </div>
